      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>This node allows the user to select the <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661783/Integrators\" data-linked-resource-id=\"19661783\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">integrator</a> needed for rendering their scene. Once chosen, it populates the UI with the relevant controls for the chosen integrator. The RenderMan documentation contains the explanation of controls for the Integrators as well as their best usage scenario.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"750\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178888/rfkSettingsPIS.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531538067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=688&amp;height=538\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178888/rfkSettingsPIS.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531538067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"538\" data-width=\"688\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178905\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkSettingsPIS.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178888\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"62149bb2-325a-46fc-89ab-c7641089e925\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178888/rfkSettingsPIS.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531538067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=688&amp;height=538 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178888/rfkSettingsPIS.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531538067&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=688&amp;height=538 1x\"></span><p>Selecting the Pxr